><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=2a950a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=6a12ffe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=0c610cfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=55d5d36a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4ba8e4ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv